These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, daffodil, amaryllis, azalea
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, cabbage, radish
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, photographer, teacher
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, parkour, water-polo
City: rome, san-francisco, paris, prague
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5
 3. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the doctor##1
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8
 9. the person traveling to prague is the person who growsaconite##1
10. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
11. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
12. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
13. the teacher is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
14. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
15. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
16. the photographer is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Flower    | azalea | daffodil     | amaryllis     | aconite |
| Food        | avocado  | artichoke | cabbage      | radish      |
| Job         | teacher  | doctor    | photographer | coach       |
| Sport       | baseball | cycling   | parkour      | water-polo  |
| City   | san-francisco      | rome  | paris   | prague      |

