 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
 8. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 9. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
10. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
12. the person eating blueberry is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
13. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is swimming##1
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
16. the person eating pepper is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
17. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's sport is soccer##1
18. the person who's sport is soccer is not the firefighter##6
19. the person who's sport is sailing is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
20. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
21. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5

