 9. the german is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
10. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the french##3
11. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the french##1
13. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the indian##8
