.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-13::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, banana, carrot, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, drawing, reading, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, musical, spy
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, daisy, aconite
City: san-francisco, marseilles, berlin, nizza
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 2. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is not to the right of the person watching animation movies##8
 5. the person eating onion is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8
 6. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
10. the person eating banana is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
13. the person watching crime movies is not the person who growsmarigold##6
14. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
15. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person eating carrot and the person who growsdaisy##2
16. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food          | banana   | asparagus   | carrot    | onion      |
| Hobby         | reading  | woodworking | baking    | drawing    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | crime       | spy       | animation  |
| Flower   | daisy | aconite   | marigold | azalea |
| City         | berlin   | marseilles     | nizza   | san-francisco   |

