.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, hiking, puzzles, reading
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, mauve, pink, blood-red
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, horror, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, goat, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, ship, train, tram
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
 3. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
 4. the person who likes blue is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
 5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 6. the person driving the train is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
 7. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
10. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who likes blue##2
11. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
12. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
13. the person who likes mauve is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
14. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
15. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
16. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |    2     |      3      |       4        |
