 1. the polish is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the indonesian##8
 5. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
