 7. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 8. the fan of r&b is not the mexican##6
 9. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of disco is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
12. the baccarat-smoker is not to the right of the fan of r&b##8
13. the chaman-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
14. the chinese is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
15. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the mexican##1
16. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
17. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
18. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
19. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
20. the fan of country is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
21. the chinese is not to the right of the mexican##8

