 7. the bartender is on the right of the software-developer##1
 8. the bartender is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person eating radish##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1
12. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the motorbike is between the baccarat-smoker and the dressmaker##2
