 1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person driving the motorbike##7
 2. the person who growsiris is between the person who growstulip and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the left of the person playing monopoly##8
 6. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
 7. the person who growsrose is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person who growsiris is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who growsiris is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing domino##2
12. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
13. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
14. the person who's sport is swimming is not the person who growsrose##6
15. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking tea##1
16. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person who growstulip##7
17. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person driving the subway##7

