 1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 2. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the chaman-smoker##7
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
 5. the person eating radish is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the siglo-smoker##5
 7. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 8. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
10. the person drinking 7up is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
12. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
14. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person eating radish##8
15. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
16. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
17. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the prince-smoker##6
18. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
19. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
20. the person eating pepper is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
