The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, april, september
 1. the owner of the snake is the fan of punk##1
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the thai##8
 4. the indian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
 6. the owner of the snake is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 7. the nigerian is not the person eating kiwi##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5
 9. the person eating tomato is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
10. the person eating kiwi is not to the left of the polish##8
11. the indian is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
14. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the thai##8
15. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
16. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
17. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the nigerian##8
18. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
19. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the hedgehog##1
20. the person who's birthday is in september is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
