 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
 2. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the game-smoker##5
 3. the alhambra-smoker is between the dutch and the fan of house##2
 4. the fan of pop is the malaysian##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the indian##5
 9. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
11. the indian is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the polish##8
13. the owner of the pony is the malaysian##1
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the fan of salsa##8
15. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the fan of house##1
16. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
